title: English Breweries, England, 2005
name: English Breweries, England, 2005
description: Here are the locations of over 500 English breweries. Nearly every microbrewery is represented, but some industrial plants of multinationals may be missing. The locations are pinpointed by postcodes.  This file is somewhat limited in that it only shows the locations of the breweries. There are no descriptions or physical addresses attached to the locations. This data was found online in kml format at http://bbs.keyhole.com/ubb/showflat.php/Cat/0/Number/518383/an/0/page/0#518383. The creator of the file sites quaffale.org.uk and ratebeer.com as his sources for brewery information.
